By The Numbers



Calgon Carbon has more than 240 patents with company scientists and engineers dedicated to developing new processes, standards, and methods. 








With 25 global offices and 17 manufacturing and reactivation facilities, the company provides solutions for hundreds of market applications.








Talented men and women across the globe, focused on delivering value through high quality products and services. 








It’s been almost 75 years since Calgon Carbon answered the government’s call to create the crucial war material known as activated carbon. 








For more than 40 years, Calgon Carbon has been at the forefront of municipal drinking water treatment. 








Our carbon technologies are used in more than 700 distinct market applications.


































